                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi>. <hi rend="italic">
Recommended to mercy by the Jury and Prosecutor.</hi>
                  </rs>—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18791020-936-punishment-50" type="punishmentDescription">
